Additional community terms (intent and conditions of use)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

1. CONTRIBUTIONS ARE WELCOME
   You may fork, modify, and submit pull requests, feature suggestions, new
   game integrations, bug fixes, and documentation improvements. Contributors
   retain copyright in their contributions and license them to the project
   under these same terms.

2. NO IMPERSONATION OR FALSE ATTRIBUTION
   You may not claim authorship of the Software as a whole or of any
   contribution you did not make. You may not redistribute the Software under
   a name that implies it is the original or an official version of
   GamePulseTracker without prior written permission from the maintainers.

3. NO ABUSE OF UPSTREAM GAME APIs
   The Software queries a number of third-party APIs (Hypixel, Wargaming,
   Jagex, Riot, Bungie, Steam, ScoreSaber, warframe.market, warframestat.us,
   gametools.network, etc.). Every operator MUST:
     (a) honour each provider's terms of service, robots.txt, and stated
         rate limits;
     (b) configure caching and back-off so that one operator's deployment
         does not degrade service for others;
     (c) NOT use this Software to scrape data the provider has explicitly
         disallowed, nor to circumvent provider rate limits, paywalls, or
         authentication;
     (d) NOT use the Software to redistribute, sell, or sublicense data
         received from a provider in violation of that provider's terms.

4. NO MALICIOUS USE
   The Software, including the companion ingest pipeline and any Overwolf
   companion built from this repo, must NOT be used to:
     - facilitate cheating in any game (e.g. wallhacks, ESP, automation
       providing a competitive advantage);
     - collect personally-identifying information about other players without
       their explicit consent;
     - hook into anti-cheat-protected processes, read protected memory, or
       inject DLLs into games;
     - distribute malware, ransomware, spyware, or any code designed to harm
       systems or users.

5. COMMUNITY PROJECT, AT YOUR OWN RISK
   This is a volunteer community project. Upstream game APIs may change,
   rate-limit your operator, or shut down without notice. Self-hosted
   operators are solely responsible for:
     - the security and uptime of their deployment;
     - the credentials they store (JWT secrets, OAuth tokens, device keys,
       database passwords);
     - the data they collect from their users;
     - compliance with applicable laws (GDPR, CCPA, etc.) in their
       jurisdiction and their users' jurisdictions;
     - the conduct of their users.

   The maintainers of GamePulseTracker are not liable for any losses or
   damages arising from your deployment, configuration, or operation of the
   Software. Any modifications you make to your own deployment are your own
   responsibility.

6. ADVERTISING + ANALYTICS
   The Software includes optional Google AdSense integration. If you enable
   it on your deployment you are solely responsible for complying with
   Google's program policies (including ads.txt placement, privacy policies,
   GDPR consent banners, etc.). The maintainers do not place any ads or
   analytics in the repository by default.

7. NO ENDORSEMENT
   References to specific games, game studios, platforms, or third-party
   services in source code, documentation, and the game catalog are factual.
   No endorsement by those parties is implied. All trademarks belong to their
   respective owners.

8. SEVERABILITY
   If any clause above is held unenforceable by a court of competent
   jurisdiction, the remaining clauses remain in full force.

